{"tid":1466851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有人入嚟！！！不如訂立標準，咩情況就點做！！！以免再被分化，被狗利用！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T17:29:01.000Z","uid":243854,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"22f9efeeb224bb66037c620453ab344564e26563","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"我唔講鬼唔鬼，成日講麻包袋，你會唔會喺咁多記者影住包呀？點解唔會呀？<span style=\"color: red;\">因為保障自己，做完都無人知邊個做囉</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警畜幾年前都玩暗角啦，係咁唔好彩俾無線影到咋嘛</span>，如果無人影到，你估有無人捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講咩民意撚，如果大家覺得國際形象唔重要嘅，咁之前咁多次賣廣告爭取支持有咩用？<br />\n嗱，實有人話之前爭取外幫手，結果？<br />\n係㗎，無用㗎，<span style=\"color: red;\">但至少外國(文明國家)無鬧過示威者先，如果連幾個文明國家都話示威者有問題，中共仲使撚驚更暴力清場？反正大家國際形象就係真暴徒，到時就算出真解放軍都係正義之師，外國話示威者有問題嘅話，佢哋真係可以出師有名保護一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n大家係焦土唔撚到㗎，我就好想佢快啲出，但絕對唔係外國認為大家係真暴徒出，因為點攬炒呀</span><br />\n<br />\n相反，面對警察用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">而家個形象係警畜亂用暴力，對比起市民反抗嘅武力簡直蚊同牛比，形象自然傾向示威者為弱者。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果係元朗黑社會，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為黑社會形象本身就係暴力邪惡，若果市民用武力對抗，形象自然係對抗惡勢力嘅正義。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但對抗一個手無吋鐵嘅人(就算係支那狗)，咁多人對付佢一個，你覺得弱者形象會去咗邊？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋而家實力唔夠，大家準備(物理，生理，心理)未完全，真係唔可以夜郎自大，應該盡量保留自身弱勢</span>(當年共匪都係保全自身，一直扮弱勢，甚至以個人名義加入國民黨，到最後打著為人民嘅旗號，召喚人民推翻國民黨，咁當然有好多仆街手段害死有錢人先)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">革命非一天完成，呢場仗我唔會話叫大家慢慢等，但有優勢嘅地方點解唔用盡？</span>我再講多次，你要對付呢啲唔係政權(強勢)形象嘅人，一係少啲人對付，唔好俾對方營造弱者形象，一係就保障安全下進行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果有更好意見請留言分享！！！大家一定要搵個共識做法，如果唔係只會不停重複呢種輪迴，到時真係唔使點捉人就散晒！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9fdf5076bfcb45646dd167c0f4f0e54a8843d562","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">幫手推下，或者諗下咩標準大家都接受到</span>"},{"pid":"efd0649f8d2bad19542b333c58eb5bfb3ede3f85","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6c6cc1ed51b8c4ed4ec57eabf227bf4c258d71","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"95b027a3022ad7c7fa1004345e435d91caea364b","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:40.000Z","msg":"喂，頭兩個鐘正評係無用㗎，幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔割席，但大家要事後討論下相同情況點做呀"},{"pid":"86d3d28abf8835c6cc2722f3b908ea001943294c","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6fe35aa1eef9095f7dcb5a0052c5fc8fe872e653","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8857dbd70bacb33db2ea0f983c80d2d876bdd19e","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4c45daee94bb82eaf5186f963c3ec6c55b47b3b","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed9b15e56b6fa47d9724528665779332bb86449","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7838b705a268b9aee53ca495cb25b884cb197603","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"549ffc17dd88e56cdb12fdbdece4168e0335ac63","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577c842299518d3df35f0378b0045b74b4e2ac0b","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"喂"},{"pid":"2592628705f094fbc36d07f107b37e9e2e536a67","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3495575225480babf80126b3b4e52890ac889297","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f33cde8858798eddd5cd5e649ae65fa0b28c2c1","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:29:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee2044108ebaf3115fd5739a49ab1b6e9f254d35","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:38:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"42d7a5f8141a896825ff6b34c9c93d629eb042a4","tid":1466851,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}